theorem Topology.P3_iff_isOpen_of_isClosed {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hA : IsClosed A) :
    Topology.P3 (A := A) ↔ IsOpen A := by
  have hclosure : closure A = A := hA.closure_eq
  constructor
  · intro hP3
    have hsubset : A ⊆ interior A := by
      intro x hx
      have : x ∈ interior (closure A) := hP3 hx
      simpa [hclosure] using this
    have heq : A = interior A := Set.Subset.antisymm hsubset interior_subset
    simpa [heq] using (isOpen_interior : IsOpen (interior A))
  · intro hOpen
    dsimp [Topology.P3]
    have h' : A ⊆ interior (closure A) := by
      have hInt : interior A ⊆ interior (closure A) := interior_mono subset_closure
      simpa [hOpen.interior_eq] using hInt
    exact h'

theorem Topology.P1_of_isOpen {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hA : IsOpen A) : Topology.P1 (A := A) := by
  dsimp [Topology.P1]
  intro x hx
  have hcl : x ∈ closure A := subset_closure hx
  simpa [hA.interior_eq] using hcl
